Package: dsreportr
Title: Data Science Report Templates
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Steven", "Eschrich", , "Steven.Eschrich@moffitt.org", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
          comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9833-2788"))
Description: A system for generating RMarkdown-based
  reports for data science applications. In particular, dsreportr provides
  necessary infrastructure for other packages to quickly implement a new, 
  derived templates without adding extra plumbing code. Or, simply override
  the YAML fields from the skeleton for one-off reports. dsreportr includes a
  markdown template for MS-Word, PDF and other output.
